WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.533 --> 00:00:04.333
Mo Yan, since you are all right

2
00:00:04.333 --> 00:00:05.466
Then I'll go first

3
00:00:05.466 --> 00:00:06.366
What's wrong, Mo Yan?

4
00:00:06.800 --> 00:00:09.000
Wasn't it fine in there just now?

5
00:00:09.100 --> 00:00:10.800
Why are you so indifferent to me now?

6
00:00:11.100 --> 00:00:13.700
Do you think I'm hiding my true identity?

7
00:00:13.700 --> 00:00:17.466
Do you mind? Actually, that's not what I'm angry about.

8
00:00:17.533 --> 00:00:18.433
I ask you

9
00:00:18.666 --> 00:00:20.700
Is what Fan Yao told you true?

10
00:00:21.066 --> 00:00:22.400
You come back to me

11
00:00:22.466 --> 00:00:24.200
Is it just to lure him out?

12
00:00:24.400 --> 00:00:25.666
There is indeed a reason for this

13
00:00:25.766 --> 00:00:27.200
But I came back for you

14
00:00:27.200 --> 00:00:28.866
Mainly because I want to marry you

15
00:00:28.900 --> 00:00:30.166
I like you.

16
00:00:30.566 --> 00:00:31.800
It's true. It's true.

17
00:00:32.866 --> 00:00:34.566
When I first met you when I was a child

18
00:00:34.666 --> 00:00:36.166
I fell in love with you

19
00:00:36.500 --> 00:00:37.500
I have sworn

20
00:00:37.966 --> 00:00:39.166
I don't want to marry you

21
00:00:39.400 --> 00:00:41.066
Just you can talk

22
00:00:41.533 --> 00:00:43.100
What happened to Zhang Ningyu?

23
00:00:43.100 --> 00:00:44.700
Ning Yu is going on a blind date that day

24
00:00:44.700 --> 00:00:46.166
Let me pretend to be his boyfriend

25
00:00:46.166 --> 00:00:47.100
If you don't believe me

26
00:00:47.100 --> 00:00:49.366
I'll call him and ask him to talk to you.

27
00:00:49.733 --> 00:00:50.633
Stop fighting.

28
00:00:51.200 --> 00:00:52.800
He has explained it to me.

29
00:00:53.000 --> 00:00:54.100
I say so

30
00:00:54.466 --> 00:00:55.833
Just to test you

31
00:00:56.466 --> 00:00:58.466
Then you believe my heart for you

32
00:00:58.966 --> 00:01:01.433
Believe but

33
00:01:02.300 --> 00:01:03.766
You are all blue

34
00:01:04.266 --> 00:01:06.766
The owner of the Infinite Hall standing on the top of the sky

35
00:01:06.966 --> 00:01:10.200
And I'm just a little star

36
00:01:10.700 --> 00:01:13.600
The identity between us is like the pen of cloud and mud

37
00:01:14.566 --> 00:01:15.900
If you marry me

38
00:01:16.600 --> 00:01:18.800
Wouldn't it be made fun of by the whole world?

39
00:01:18.800 --> 00:01:19.900
Two people together

40
00:01:19.900 --> 00:01:22.300
The most important thing is to see if there is each other in your heart

41
00:01:22.466 --> 00:01:23.633
It's not identity.

42
00:01:24.100 --> 00:01:26.200
And the woman I, Xiao Wuji, want to marry

43
00:01:26.200 --> 00:01:27.666
Who dares to make irresponsible remarks

